---
import PageShell from "../components/PageShell.astro";
---

<PageShell
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Al Tareen collects, uses, and protects your information."
  hidePageHead={false}
>
  <section class="legalPage" aria-label="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="legalContainer">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="effective">Effective Date: March 20, 2026</p>

      <p>
        At <strong>Al Tareen</strong> (https://altareen.com), your privacy is important.
        This Privacy Policy outlines how information is collected, used, and protected
        when you access or interact with this website. By using this website, you agree
        to the terms described in this policy.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Automatically collected data:</strong> IP address, browser type,
          device information, cookies, and usage data for analytics and performance.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Voluntarily provided data:</strong> Name, email address, and any additional information when
          submitted through the contact form.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>Your information is used to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Analyze website traffic and usage patterns</li>
        <li>Improve content, features, and overall user experience</li>
        <li>Respond to inquiries or communications</li>
        <li>Support future product, service, or marketing initiatives (if applicable)</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Your information is <strong>never sold, rented, or traded</strong> to third parties.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
      <p>
        This website may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance
        user experience and analyze performance.
      </p>
      <p>
        Third-party services such as analytics providers (e.g., Google Analytics)
        may be used to better understand user behavior.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings or request
        deletion by contacting us.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Personal data is retained only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes
        outlined in this policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may request:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request removal of your personal data</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        To make a request, contact:
        <a href="mailto:altareenk@outlook.com">altareenk@outlook.com</a>
      </p>

      <h2>6. Children’s Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This website is not intended for individuals under the age of 13.
        No personal information is knowingly collected from children.
      </p>

      <h2>7. External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This website may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible
        for the privacy practices or content of those third-party sites.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Any updates will be reflected
        by the revised effective date above.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For any questions regarding this Privacy Policy:
        <a href="mailto:altareenk@outlook.com">altareenk@outlook.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

<style is:global>
  html, body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .legalPage {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 0 64px;
    display: flow-root;
  }

  .legalContainer {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--border) 74%, transparent);
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 98%, white 2%),
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 98%, black 2%)
      );
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.62) inset,
      0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.018);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .effective {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 12px 18px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
  }

  a:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  /* Fix header logo unwanted styling */
  header a,
  .logo {
    border: none !important;
    background: transparent !important;
    box-shadow: none !important;
  }

  /* Remove underline from footer links */
  footer a {
    text-decoration: none !important;
    border-bottom: none !important;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .legalContainer {
      padding: 16px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
</PageShell>